   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can import the benefit line items containing top line product and child products for each section when the bundle saving program is in Draft or Amendment status.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To import each section to your program:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Navigate to the Qualifications &amp; Benefits tab of your program.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Expand the section.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Import</b> icon (<image height="19"
                   placement="inline"
                   href="../attachments/102432715/102432728.png"
                   class="- topic/image "/>). The import popup opens.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Choose a File</b>.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Select a .csv file from your local drive.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Import</b>.</li>
      </ol>
